<!-- General / Medical and Coaching Services -->
<section class="section section-alt" id="general">
  <div class="container faq-container">
    <h2 class="faq-section-title">Medical &amp; Coaching Services</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>What services are offered by Dr. Linda Bluestein, the Hypermobility MD?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Dr. Bluestein is currently accepting new clients for <strong>EduCoaching</strong>, which combines personalized information with one-on-one coaching. All sessions are live, interactive video calls with Dr. Bluestein. EduCoaching is available worldwide through Bendy Bodies, LLC.</p>
        <p>She is also accepting a very limited number of new <strong>patients</strong> for medical services. You can join the waiting list by completing the patient intake form on the <a href="/services/">Services</a> page.</p>
        <p>Dr. Bluestein is also the founder and host of the <a href="/podcast/">Bendy Bodies Podcast</a>, featuring expert conversations on hypermobility and related conditions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>Does Hypermobility MD offer virtual appointments?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes. Virtual appointments are available for EduCoaching clients and for some patient follow-up visits. New and existing EduCoaching clients can schedule through Bendy Bodies, LLC. Existing patients can schedule through the patient portal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>What are the payment options?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Clients and patients are directly responsible for payment. We accept credit cards and Venmo (@Linda-Bluestein).</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>What is the difference between being a patient and being an EduCoaching client?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p><strong>Medical Services (Patient):</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Patients must meet Dr. Bluestein in person for their first appointment in Colorado or Wisconsin</li>
          <li>Dr. Bluestein can write prescriptions, order lab work, and order imaging</li>
          <li>Follow-up visits can be virtual for up to one year (patients must reside in CO or WI)</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>EduCoaching (Client):</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Clients can live anywhere in the world</li>
          <li>No travel is needed &mdash; all sessions are conducted online one-on-one</li>
          <li>Dr. Bluestein provides information and guidance to work with your local healthcare team</li>
          <li>Dr. Bluestein cannot write prescriptions or order lab work/imaging in this setting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>How does Hypermobility MD create an environment where a diverse range of patients and clients feel comfortable seeking care?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Hypermobility MD is dedicated to fostering an inclusive atmosphere, recognizing the potential disparities in healthcare &mdash; especially for chronic and complex conditions. Every patient and client is treated with respect, sincerity, and empathy, receiving considerate and tailored care.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Medical Services -->
<section class="section" id="medical">
  <div class="container faq-container">
    <h2 class="faq-section-title">Medical Services</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>Is Hypermobility MD currently accepting new patients?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Hypermobility MD accepts a very small number of patients, and you can join the waiting list by completing the intake form on the <a href="/services/">Services</a> page. Prefer not to wait? Dr. Bluestein is accepting new clients for <a href="/services/#coaching">EduCoaching</a> through Bendy Bodies, LLC.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>What medical treatments does Hypermobility MD offer?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Current patients are evaluated at each visit and prescribed a comprehensive treatment plan which may include medications, supplements, physical therapy, and occupational therapy. Laboratory studies and imaging will be ordered where medically indicated.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>How do I know which medical package to choose?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We offer three session options to fit different needs:</p>
        <p><strong>Gold Package</strong> (Least Intensive)</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Best for routine check-ups or a specific, limited health concern</li>
          <li>Typically 90 minutes for the first appointment and 25 minutes for follow-up</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Platinum Package</strong> (Moderate Intensity)</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Designed for patients who need a deeper review or have multiple related concerns</li>
          <li>Typically 150 minutes for the first appointment and 50 minutes for follow-up</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Diamond Package</strong> (Most Intensive)</p>
        <ul>
          <li>For thorough evaluations, extensive assessments, or complex medical histories</li>
          <li>Recommended for most patients with EDS, HSD, POTS, and MCAS</li>
          <li>Typically 210 minutes for the first appointment and 90 minutes for follow-up</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Coaching Services -->
<section class="section section-alt" id="coaching">
  <div class="container faq-container">
    <h2 class="faq-section-title">Coaching Services</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>What is EduCoaching?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>EduCoaching is a unique process developed by Dr. Bluestein that combines personalized information with one-on-one coaching. All sessions are live, interactive video calls with Dr. Bluestein, available worldwide through Bendy Bodies, LLC.</p>
        <p>Through EduCoaching, you receive information and guidance to help you self-manage your condition. You will learn how to advocate for yourself more effectively in healthcare settings. Dr. Bluestein empowers you to receive better healthcare from your own medical team, coaches you through the health, dietary, and emotional aspects of these conditions, and provides specific suggestions for improving the quality of your life.</p>
        <p><em>Coaching services are for educational and informational purposes only and do not take the place of medical care. Dr. Bluestein will not be able to prescribe medications or order laboratory testing in this setting.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>What are the differences between the EduCoaching session levels, and which one is right for me?</span>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p><strong>Bronze</strong> (20 minutes) &mdash; Personalized one-on-one coaching focused on a single issue.</p>
        <p><strong>Silver</strong> (45 minutes) &mdash; Includes everything in Bronze, plus:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Detailed review of 2&ndash;3 issues</li>
          <li>Review of up to 10 pages of medical records</li>
          <li>Discount code for supplements</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Gold</strong> (100 minutes) &mdash; Includes everything in Silver, plus:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Review of complex, multi-system problems</li>
          <li>Review of up to 30 pages of medical records</li>
          <li>Complimentary follow-up call (up to 15 minutes) within 30 days</li>
          <li>Custom handouts designed by Dr. Bluestein</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Platinum</strong> (100 minutes) &mdash; Includes everything in Gold, plus:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Peer-to-peer consultation with your primary care provider (up to 15 minutes)</li>
          <li>Access to Dr. Bluestein&rsquo;s trusted resources</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Professional Mentorship -->
<section class="section" id="mentorship">
  <div class="container faq-container">
    <h2 class="faq-section-title">Professional Mentorship</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
